
glslShader
---------

Provides a wrapper for GLSL (OpenGL's shading language) to simplify using of
shader programs in your applications. Syntax is similar to Nvidia's Cg, so
it will be no problem to work with GLSL instead.


see glslShader.h for the functions available from the library.

-- Art Tevs <tevs@mpi-sb.mpg.de>
